{"tid":2121934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"190米外雷射筆照警署 經理獲判100小時服務令","createTime":"2020-07-23T15:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T16:41:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dcacbe99e6bd1b40bf1f99d4264ba258b34b150b","tid":2121934,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200723/JQHUIFQYNHVUTFF22MLKJFJDSU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FJQHUIFQYNHVUTFF22MLKJFJDSU%2F&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=219300a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FJQHUIFQYNHVUTFF22MLKJFJDSU%2F&h=a288a034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200723/JQHUIFQYNHVUTFF22MLKJFJDSU/</a><br />\n<br />\n銀行經理今年元旦在將軍澳景林邨，在距離約190米外用雷射筆照射將軍澳警署內站崗警員，令警員眼部不適，無法站崗。涉案經理早前承認一項管有攻擊性武器罪，案件今於觀塘裁判法院判刑。署理主任裁判官徐綺薇指被告的報告內容正面，他亦有悔意，其家人也相當支持他，決定根據感化官建議，判處100小時社會服務令。"},{"pid":"66e0a9bb14e23d539c20621e516c508dec820d50","tid":2121934,"uid":55493,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T15:55:42.000Z","msg":"點解照警署犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好以為判100小時叫良心輕判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲野根本唔應該有懲罰"},{"pid":"18fb39e13b57e5076a0f859fb53c57110f611e14","tid":2121934,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T15:59:16.000Z","msg":"真係好撚弱雞，見到聽日個太陽你真係要感謝主"},{"pid":"50433cc222773469bbca9c2306c2691c3c8c6d45","tid":2121934,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T15:59:23.000Z","msg":"在距離約190米外用雷射筆照射將軍澳警署內站崗警員，令警員眼部不適，無法站崗。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b906a98371ed0c782074fb35c14777166052d0","tid":2121934,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited